item.title: FirstImpressions
item.description: These are my thoughts, I’m basing these on what I have heard, read or experienced - if I am misinformed, I am sorry - correct me, by all means but I am not purposfully spouting my own brand of nonsense or mistruth. Let me know and I’ll try to edit where I am wrong Try Go - These are my impressions after using Golang as my main language for 6 weeks If you came upon Go recently the chances are you’ve come upon the Tour of Go.
